Classic vs. Modern Gamertags

Not all Xbox names are created equal. There are two main types:

• Classic Gamertags
These are the originals. Think short, clean names like "SniperWolf" or "TacticalToast." No numbers, no suffixes—just pure, iconic vibes. The catch? Most of these are long gone.

